---
title: Prawn and Sweet Potato Pasanda Spiced Curry with Cumin Rice and Flaked Almonds
description: Pasanda curries are fragrant and gently spiced Indian dishes that are usually rich and creamy. Here, we've got prawns, sweet potato, peas and cumin rice, perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the pasanda curry sauce.
